\c 20
\s Ukugula kukaHezekhiya
\p
\v 1 Ngalezonsuku uHezekhiya wagula okokufa\x + 2 Lan. 32.24. Isa. 38.1-8,21,22.\x*. UIsaya indodana kaAmozi umprofethi wasefika kuye wathi kuye: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Laya indlu yakho, ngoba uzakufa, kawuyikuphila.
\v 2 Wasephendulela ubuso bakhe emdulini, wakhuleka eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 1 Sam. 20.25.\x* esithi:
\v 3 Ngiyakuncenga N\nd kosi\nd*, ake ukhumbule ukuthi ngihambe phambi kwakho ngobuqotho\x + Neh. 5.19.13. 14,22,31.\x* langenhliziyo epheleleyo\x + 1 Kho. 8.61.\x*, ngenza okulungileyo emehlweni akho\x + 18.3.\x*. UHezekhiya wasekhala inyembezi ngokukhala okukhulu\x + Hlab. 39.13.\x*.
\v 4 Kwasekusithi uIsaya engakaphumi egumeni elingaphakathi, ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lafika kuye lisithi:
\v 5 Buyela uthi kuHezekhiya umbusi wabantu bami\x + 1 Sam. 9.16. 10.1.\x*: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaDavida uyihlo: Ngiwuzwile umkhuleko wakho\x + 19.20. Hlab. 65.2.\x*, ngabona inyembezi zakho\x + Hlab. 39.12. 56.8.\x*; khangela, ngizakusilisa; ngosuku lwesithathu uzakwenyukela endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 6 Njalo ngizakwengezelela iminyaka elitshumi lanhlanu ensukwini zakho; ngikukhulule wena lalumuzi esandleni senkosi yeAsiriya; ngiwuvikele lumuzi ngenxa yami langenxa yenceku yami uDavida\x + 19.34.\x*.
\p
\v 7 UIsaya wasesithi: Thathani isigaqa somkhiwa\x + Isa. 38.21.\x*. Basebesithatha, basifaka phezu kwethumba, yasisila\x + Levi 13.18.\x*.
\p
\v 8 UHezekhiya wasesithi kuIsaya: Yisiphi isibonakaliso sokuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* izangisilisa, lokuthi ngizakwenyukela endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd* ngosuku lwesithathu\x + 19.29.\x*?
\v 9 UIsaya wasesithi: Lesi yisibonakaliso kuwe esivela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni esokuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* izayenza into eyikhulumileyo: Isithunzi sizakuya phambili izinyathelo ezilitshumi, loba siye emuva izinyathelo ezilitshumi yini?
\v 10 UHezekhiya wasesithi: Kulula\x + 3.18.\x* esithunzini ukuthi selule izinyathelo ezilitshumi; hatshi, kodwa isithunzi kasibuyele emuva izinyathelo ezilitshumi\x + Hlab. 102.11.\x*.
\v 11 UIsaya umprofethi wasekhala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, yasibuyisela emuva isithunzi, ngezinyathelo esasehle ngazo esikhwelweni sikaAhazi, izinyathelo ezilitshumi emuva.
\s Inkosi yeBhabhiloni ithuma izithunywa kuHezekhiya
\p
\v 12 Ngalesosikhathi uMerodaki-Baladani indodana kaBaladani, inkosi yeBhabhiloni, wathumela izincwadi lesipho kuHezekhiya, ngoba wayezwile ukuthi uHezekhiya ubekade egula\x + Isa. 39.1-8.\x*.
\v 13 UHezekhiya wabalalela\x + Isa. 39.2. 2 Lan. 32.31.\x*, wabatshengisa yonke indlu yakhe yezinto eziligugu, isiliva legolide lamakha lamafutha amahle lendlu yezikhali zakhe, lakho konke okwakutholakala endlini yakhe yokuligugu; kakulalutho endlini yakhe lembusweni wonke wakhe uHezekhiya angabatshengisanga lona.
\p
\v 14 UIsaya umprofethi wasesiza enkosini uHezekhiya wathi kiyo: Batheni lababantu? Futhi bebevela ngaphi besiza kuwe? UHezekhiya wasesithi: Bebevela elizweni elikhatshana, eBhabhiloni.
\v 15 Wasesithi: Baboneni endlini yakho? UHezekhiya wasesithi: Babone konke okusendlini yami; kakulalutho phakathi kokuligugu kwami engingabatshengisanga khona\x + 20.13.\x*.
\v 16 UIsaya wasesithi kuHezekhiya: Zwana ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 17 Khangela, insuku ziyeza lapho konke okusendlini yakho lalokho oyihlo abakubekelelayo kuze kube lamuhla kuzathwalelwa eBhabhiloni; kakuyikusala lutho, itsho iN\nd kosi\x + 25.13. 24.13. Jer. 20.5. Jer. 27.19-22. 52.17.\x*\nd*.
\v 18 Njalo bazathatha emadodaneni akho azaphuma kuwe, ozawazala, abe ngabathenwa esigodlweni senkosi yeBhabhiloni\x + 24.12. 2 Lan. 33.11.\x*.
\v 19 UHezekhiya wasesithi kuIsaya: Lihle ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* olikhulumileyo. Wasesithi: Kaku\add njalo\add* yini, uba kuzakuba khona ukuthula lokuvikeleka ensukwini zami\x + 1 Sam. 3.18. 2 Lan. 32.25,26.\x*?
\s Ukufa kukaHezekhiya
\p
\v 20 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaHezekhiya, lawo wonke amandla akhe\x + 2 Lan. 32.32.\x*, lokuthi wenza ichibi, lomgelo\x + 18.17. Neh. 2.14. 3.16.\x*, wangenisa amanzi phakathi komuzi, kakubhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoJuda\x + 2 Lan. 32.30. Isa. 22.9,11.\x*?
\v 21 UHezekhiya waselala laboyise. UManase indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe\x + 2 Lan. 32.33.\x*.
